CAVAL,is,an,initiative,for,developing,open,standards,for,data,interoperability,in,the,travel,and,tourism,industry,The,CAVAL,specifications,consist,of,a,set,of,XML,schemas,and,WSDL,endpoints,along,with,guidelines,for,deploying,RESTful,services,Services,that,CAVAL,has,already,developed,using,its,specifications,include,the,commons,booking,hotel,booking,transfer,booking,destination,activity,booking,and,channel,manager,services,These,services,are,all,accessible,using,SOAP,calls,issued,in,XML,format